{"id":24,"parent_id":0,"book_id":0,"content_id":1,"language_id":0,"display_order":24,"title":"The New Adventures of Matt and Mandy","subtitle":"","short_title":"The New Adventures of Matt and Mandy","uri":"/friend/2013/04/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy","content":[["div",{"id":"head1","uri":"/friend/2013/04/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.head1"},[".title","The New Adventures of Matt & Mandy"]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"f1","uri":"/friend/2013/04/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f1"},[".credit",["div",{"id":"p2","uri":"/friend/2013/04/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p2"},"Illustrations by Maryn Roos"]],["div",{"id":"p3","uri":"/friend/2013/04/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p3"},"Matt and Mandy and their parents have moved to a new town and a new home. Now they are going to their new ward for the first time."]],["div",{"id":"f2","uri":"/friend/2013/04/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f2"},["div",{"id":"p4","uri":"/friend/2013/04/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p4"},"Dad says it’s natural to be nervous, but if I act friendly, other people will be friendly too."]],["div",{"id":"f3","uri":"/friend/2013/04/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f3"},["div",{"id":"p5","uri":"/friend/2013/04/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p5"},"This looks kinda the same … but kinda different too."],["div",{"id":"p6","uri":"/friend/2013/04/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p6"},"But I feel good here, like going into the chapel at home. I mean, our",["span.emphasis","old"],"home."]],["div",{"id":"f4","uri":"/friend/2013/04/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f4"},["div",{"id":"p7","uri":"/friend/2013/04/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p7"},"I recognize the songs from our old ward."]],["div",{"id":"f5","uri":"/friend/2013/04/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f5"},["div",{"id":"p8","uri":"/friend/2013/04/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p8"},"The sacrament’s exactly the same, and Mom always says that’s what we’re really here for."]],["div",{"id":"f6","uri":"/friend/2013/04/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f6"},["div",{"id":"p9","uri":"/friend/2013/04/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p9"},"Hi, we’re the Coopers. We just moved into the ward."],["div",{"id":"p10","uri":"/friend/2013/04/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p10"},"Hi, my name’s Mandy Cooper. We just moved in."],["div",{"id":"p11","uri":"/friend/2013/04/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p11"},"Man, I’ll sure be glad when I’m taller."]],["div",{"id":"f7","uri":"/friend/2013/04/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f7"},["div",{"id":"p12","uri":"/friend/2013/04/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p12"},"This is Sister Rogers, the Primary president. She’ll introduce you to your teachers. And Dad and I will meet you here right after the meetings."]],["div",{"id":"f8","uri":"/friend/2013/04/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f8"},["div",{"id":"p13","uri":"/friend/2013/04/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p13"},"Hmmm. People here are nice too."],["div",{"id":"p14","uri":"/friend/2013/04/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p14"},"This really",["span.emphasis","isn’t"],"so hard after all."]],["div",{"id":"p15","uri":"/friend/2013/04/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p15"},"(To be continued.)"]]],"refs":null}
